lead_paragraph: Another productive outing by their bench allowed the Los Angeles Clippers to bolt past Chicago on Sunday, with reserve guard Jamal Crawford scoring 26 points in a 120-93 blowout of the Bulls at Staples Center.

headline.print_headline: Clippers' Bench the Difference in Win Over Bulls
